00:07.441 --> 00:09.842
¶ That started
    from this tropic port ¶

00:09.910 --> 00:12.076
¶ Aboard this tiny ship ¶

00:12.145 --> 00:14.412
¶ The mate was a mighty
    sailin' man ¶

00:14.481 --> 00:16.782
¶ The Skipper brave and sure ¶

00:16.851 --> 00:19.284
